{"tid":2119188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警長涉食宵夜時打傷勸交女警　辯方將去信律政司商其他方式處理","createTime":"2020-07-22T03:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T03:27:13.000Z","uid":291865,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fffa11d66dde4771d0a2455d74e8597593a3a2bb","tid":2119188,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"十名休班警員於今年 4 月 19 日凌晨在元朗一間食肆「食宵夜」期間，當中一名警長與警員發生口角，一名女警上前勸交。該名警長被指以玻璃樽及手打傷她的頭部，被控一項普通襲擊罪，案件今（22 日）於屯門裁判法院再提堂。辯方申請將案件押至 8 月 12 日再訊，以等候被告的醫療報告，及去信律政司商討以其他方式處理，期間被告獲准以原有條件繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告梁珏榮，40歲，報稱警長，被控一項普通襲擊罪，控罪指他於 4 月 19 日在元朗屏會街 13-17 號屏會中心外行人路上，襲擊女子蘇伶雅。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC926/2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/警長涉食宵夜時打傷勸交女警-辯方將去信律政司商其他方式處理/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%B5%E5%A4%9C%E6%99%82%E6%89%93%E5%82%B7%E5%8B%B8%E4%BA%A4%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%87%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%95%86%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB3obfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=4451031d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%B5%E5%A4%9C%E6%99%82%E6%89%93%E5%82%B7%E5%8B%B8%E4%BA%A4%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%87%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%95%86%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%2F&h=a73a5178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/警長涉食宵夜時打傷勸交女警-辯方將去信律政司商其他方式處理/</a>"},{"pid":"1a41e83f3d966241108625a083acca81b9e786ab","tid":2119188,"uid":168567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法<br />\n除非你係警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d8398a3dbe215fdfc9d197ead72094915a46f5","tid":2119188,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":